public class isawLineProfileLayout
extends gov.noaa.noaaserver.sgt.awt.GraphicLayout

isawLineProfileLayout creates a pre-defined graphics layout for profile data using LineCartesianGraph. This layout is application specific.

See Also:
LineCartesianGraph, Serialized Form
